== Borders ==

[[Image:EEZ Cape Verde.png|thumb|Map of Cape Verde's EEZ.]]

Cape Verde shares [[maritime boundary|maritime boundaries]] with [[Mauritania]] and [[Senegal]]. Cape Verde has signed [[Treaty|treaties]] with [[Cape Verde – Senegal Maritime Delimitation Treaty|Senegal]] and [[Cape Verde – Mauritania Maritime Delimitation Treaty|Mauritania]] [[boundary delimitation|delimiting]] the specific boundaries. However, the two treaties conflict in their delimitation of the precise borders.

== Climate ==
{{See also|Cape Verde#Geography and climate}}
