== Visiting the ecoregion ==

The higher altitudes of the islands are accessible on the islands of [[Fogo, Cape Verde|Fogo]], where there is a road to the volcano and walks up to the crater, and the mountainous [[Santo Antão, Cape Verde|Santo Antão]] where there are hiking routes.

== Extreme points ==
* Northernmost Point - [[Ponta do Sol, Cape Verde|Ponta do Sol]] on [[Santo Antão, Cape Verde|Santao Antão]] Island
* Southernmost point - [[Ponta Nho Martinho]] on [[Brava, Cape Verde|Brava]]
* Westernmost point - [[Ponta Chao de Mongrade]] on [[Santo Antão, Cape Verde|Santao Antão]]*
* Easternmost point - a cape about 5&nbsp;km ESE of [[Tarales]] on [[Boa Vista, Cape Verde|Boa Vista]] island

* *''Note: this is also the westernmost point of Africa''

